SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" LEFT OUTER JOIN "mentions" ON "mentions"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "statuses" "reblog" ON "reblog"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "reblog"."id" = "statuses"."reblog_of_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "reblog"."account_id" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND ("statuses"."visibility" IN ($2, $3) OR "mentions"."account_id" = $4) AND ("statuses"."reblog_of_id" IS NULL OR ("accounts"."domain" IS NULL OR 1=1) AND 1=1) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND (statuses.reply = FALSE OR statuses.in_reply_to_account_id = statuses.account_id) GROUP BY "statuses"."id" ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
